rwell prize, said the journalism shortlist \"features journalism that hums with vivid language and clear thought\" and that the judges \"were heartened by the adventurous and brave reporting put forward this year.\"</p><p><em>Source:</em> <a href=\"http://theorwellprize.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Shortlist-2014-press-release.pdf\">Orwell Prize</a></p>","headline":"Seven journalists shortlisted for Orwell prize for journalism","trailText":"<p>Three journalists also nominated for books prize</p>","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"theguardian.com","showInRelatedContent":"true","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3zyxf","wordcount":"214","commentable":"true","internalContentCode":"435289706","allowUgc":"false","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Roy Greenslade","internalPageCode":"2082066","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-05-02T07:41:00Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade/2014/apr/25/orwellprize-awards-and-prizes","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/media/greenslade/2014/apr/25/orwellprize-awards-and-prizes","tags":[{"id":"media/greenslade","webTitle":"Greenslade","description":"Roy Greenslade's Guardian blog on politics, news and the media","type":"blog","sectionId":"media","sectionName":"Media","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/media/greenslade","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/media/greenslade","references":[]},{"id":"media/media","webTitle":"Media","type":"keyword","sectionId":"media","sectionName":"Media","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/media/media","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/media/media","references":[]},{"id":"tone/blog","webTitle":"Blogposts","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/blog","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/tone/blog","references":[]},{"id":"profile/roygreenslade","webTitle":"Roy Greenslade","rcsId":"GNL016410","r2ContributorId":"16378","bylineImageUrl":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/P